org.jscsi.target.scsi.sense.senseDataDescriptor

Enum SenseDataDescriptorType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SenseDataDescriptorType>
      • org.jscsi.target.scsi.sense.senseDataDescriptor.SenseDataDescriptorType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<SenseDataDescriptorType>

    public enum SenseDataDescriptorType
extends Enum<SenseDataDescriptorType>
    The SenseDataDescriptorType is part of a SenseDataDescriptor and determines the object's (non-abstract sub)class.

    Vendor specific sense data descriptors types (values 0x80 to 0xff) and respective SenseDataDescriptors are not implemented!

    Author:
    Andreas Ergenzinger
